dct_description_sm: Inset: Relief map of Beijing region (1:250,000). Map shows administrative boundaries; governmental/ institutional, comercial/industrial and population density areas by color code. "505393 12-82." Indexes and glossary on verso. Map is companion to 5 more sheet covering the Beijing area. PrEx 3.10/4:B 39/2/sheet 1-6. Inset: Beijng environs (1:250,000). Verso: Index to numbered features identified on map:"505393 12-82 " One map in six sheets. [United States. Central Intelligence Agency]
